Reuse across the same domain (Objective 2)
1 Percentage of LOV domain ontologies that reused other ontologies
apart from their modules: 72.80%.
2 The percentage of these ontologies such that some of the ontologies
they reused belonged to the same LOV category as themself: 19.92%.
Hypothesis 1 is valid =⇒Most of the ontologies do not reuse
